casebody.data:
In re Department of Public Parks. In re O’Brien. (Supreme Court, General Term, First Department. December 2, 1889.) Motion to confirm report of commissioners of estimate.

Argued before Van Brunt,P. J., and Barrett and Cullen, JJ.

Wm. H. Clark, for the Department of Public Parks. Andrew A. Henderson, for Maria O’Brien. Per Curiam.

Report sent back to commissioners for revision.
